name: Toad Poems — CHAPBOOK
description:
A beautiful letterpress printed little chapbook by Incline Press.

Toad Poems, contains two poems: Mr.Toad by Kenneth Grahame and Warty Bliggens by Don Marquis, for which I did a couple of illustrations.

dimensions: 210mm x 105mm
6 pages, hand sewn
Letterpress printed, with hand colour tinted illustrations
with Ingres paper stock folded cover

name: Jabberwocky — PAMPHLET
description:
A letterpress printed pamphlet - the Jabberwocky poem 
from Lewis Carroll's Through the Looking-Glass
with a full page illustration block printed in the centre.
Printed and published by Incline Press 

Size: 225mm x 130mm

name: Women Who Run with Scissors — PAMPHLET
description:
Alice Smith & Nina McNamara

A visual diatribe of imagery, cut up from the history of women's magazines and their manipulating effect on women.

'Taught from infancy that beauty is woman's sceptre, the mind shapes itself to the body, and roaming round its gilt cage, only seeks to adorn its prison.'
Mary Wollstonecraft

210mm x 148mm, 24 pages, hand sewn.
Risograph printed on Stockwell 160gsm with trace paper fly leaves. Hahnemühle Bugra Butten 130gsm soft pink cover and letterpress printed title.
Hand numbered edition of 100
